author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description: Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! I was away this weekend and missed the live coverage of the most evil scammers I've ever seen in the world of crypto. We've reached a point where cryptobros feel it's okay to steal from a person suffering from stage 4 cancer and feel somehow it's okay. Heartless stuff.
title: This Should Make You Mad...
